fields.label: Venue name, information, or contact person.
fields.desc_text:
Fire
performance has specific requirements for staging areas and general
location. If you are unsure if your city / venue allows fire
performance, we can help figure it out. Please provide us with the name
of venue or an address. Providing a map location will also help us
estimate travel time.
